title: Archibald's Next Big Thing Is Here!
overview: Archibald's Next Big Thing Is Here! is the next chapter for Archibald Strutter, a chicken who "yes-and's" his way through life. While his adventures don't always go as planned, Archibald takes it one step at a time with the help of his three siblings, Sage, Finly, and Loy, and his trusty sidekick, Bea.
